Alternately, you can stream _x_, utilizing the _[limit](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#limit(long))_, _[mapToDouble](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/Stream.html#mapToDouble(java.util.function.ToDoubleFunction))_ and _[min](https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/20/docs/api/java.base/java/util/stream/DoubleStream.html#min())_ methods.

```java
public static double findMinVolume(Solids[]x,int xlast){
    return
        Stream.of(x)
              .limit(xlast - 1)
              .mapToDouble(Solids::getVolume)
              .min()
              .getAsDouble();
}
